<div class="content px-5">
  <h2 class="text-center mb-4 header mt-3">Offer Letter for Employment</h2>

  <p class="mt-5 mb-2"><strong>Date:</strong> <%= (@document&.start_date - 5.days)&.strftime('%d %B %Y') %></p>

  <p><strong>Dear <%= @document.user.name.titleize %>,</strong></p>

  <p class="mt-5 mb-2">
    This is with reference to your application and subsequent interview held at our office.
    We are pleased to offer you a position as <strong><%= @document.start_position.titleize %></strong> and your compensation will be <strong>Rs <%= @document.ctc.round %>/- per annum</strong> as discussed and mutually agreed.
  </p>

  <p class="mb-2">
    Further, as discussed, you are expected to join us on or before
    <strong><%= @document&.start_date&.strftime('%d %B %Y') %></strong> at our office. Please bring the following documents at the time of your joining:
  </p>

  <ul class="mt-3">
    <li>Four passport size photographs</li>
    <li>Qualification Certificates (originals with one photocopy set; originals will be returned after verification)</li>
    <li>Proof of residence</li>
    <li>Photocopies of your Resignation Letter and the Relieving Letter from your current employer</li>
    <li>Photocopy of your last drawn salary slip</li>
    <li>Aadhar Card</li>
    <li>PAN Card</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="lh-lg mt-4">
    A detailed appointment letter along with the terms and conditions of your appointment will be
    issued to you upon joining the company. Please send us a confirmation as a token of your acceptance
    of this offer letter.
  </p>

  <p class="mt-4 mb-2">Thanks and Regards,</p>
  <p class="mb-2"><strong>HR Department</strong></p>
  <p><strong>Technomatz IT Solutions Pvt Ltd.</strong></p>

  <p class="disclaimer mb-3">
    *This is a computer-generated offer letter; signature or seal is not required.
  </p>
</div>
